                <head>No. 633.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Maynard</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Fish</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Constantinople</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1875-08-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">August</hi> 16, 1875</date>. (Received August
                        16.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="flushleft">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Fish</hi>, Washington:</p>
                <p>Saturday, Porte, informed by Aristarchi, telegraphed governor, ordering
                    reparation made American consul before Hartford reaches Tripoli.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>MAYNARD.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
